description:
A DLC pack for GROOVE COASTER WAI WAI PARTY!!!! that includes 10 songs, navigators, and avatars from "CHUNITHM"!

This pack includes the following content.
■Song Pack (10 songs)
 - Ikazuchi / Takenobu Mitsuyoshi
 - Paqqin / owl*tree
 - Nemurenuyo kimiwo omofu / baker
 - World Vanquisher / void(Mournfinale)
 - Xevel / Tatsh
 - Summer is over / TORIENA
 - Trrricksters!! / s-don vs. Hino Isuka
 - Cosmo Pop Funclub / NayutalieN
 - YukiOtoko / Kaneko Chiharu
 - ???(Secret)

■Navigator
 - CHUNI-PENGUIN *with voice(CV:Ayaka Maekawa)
 - SHONI-PENGUIN *with voice(CV:Ayaka Maekawa)

■Avatar
 - CHUNI-PENGUIN(2D)
 - SHONI-PENGUIN(2D)
 - Magellan Magellan(2D)
 - Lichtschütze(2D)
 - Nai(2D)
 - MDA-01【Sirius】(2D)

*Some content will be unlocked via missions after downloading.
name: CHUNITHM Pack
